Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:17.20,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 嫁给了曾是钢琴家的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:22.21,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我出生后不久 他们就分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:26.64,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢你爸爸了 他已经江郎才尽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:31.05,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂树 只有你 不能背叛妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.84,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈给我带来了很棒的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:37.72,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的小孩 只会耽误我学习音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.61,0:00:41.75,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹钢琴时 我们总在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:45.57,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈最喜欢有才华的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:49.18,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久 妈妈就和一位炙手可热的作曲家再婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:51.18,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 我的弟弟出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:57.80,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都未曾发现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:00:59.87,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 我马上就察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:01.83,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:05.98,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈最喜欢有天赋的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.34,0:01:10.90,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去 我就会被这世界抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.75,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 时间 请为我驻足
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:18.78,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停在我还是最棒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:24.11,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样 妈妈就会安慰我说 你才是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.76,0:01:28.17,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至 妈妈可能会比往常更爱我这个可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:37.07,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂树 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:41.65,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次的比赛 你弟弟一定会获得冠军的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:44.42,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈最爱才了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:50.24,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 鸟笼生了锈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:54.86,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 小鸟再也不能飞向外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:57.61,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:28.23,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我已不能再弹刚琴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.34,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手已经受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.07,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.29,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去命运指引的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:43.26,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:53.30,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上你就会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.35,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果 你可得看仔细了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:03.20,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚 我是为何而生 又是为何要向高仓家报仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:13.43,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 必须在入夜之前将阳毬送回医院
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.72,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗老师 这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.68,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过 那已经是过去的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:23.35,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会对高仓他们抱有特殊的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:25.74,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:27.64,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样 多蕗老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:30.11,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇又有何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:32.01,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在那里看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.14,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是你的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:37.70,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马 找到阳毬了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.30,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是高仓冠叶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:41.95,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.29,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.21,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我唐突地说一句 我绑架了你的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.53,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我放了她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:52.44,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把你父亲带到我的面前来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.09,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:56.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地图 我会发送给你 你还是早点来的好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.64,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经等得有点心烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:05.40,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高仓的父亲 不是已经失踪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.55,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:11.81,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你怎么让冠叶把他的父亲带来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:13.88,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:18.09,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 如果冠叶的父亲真的来了 你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.37,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是确认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:22.86,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认 你姐姐桃果…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:28.09,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我活下去的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:42.05,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.90,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是小孩回收站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.28,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩回收站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被世界遗弃的孩子聚集的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.28,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:59.43,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我已经被妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.60,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 我们会变成透明的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:05.40,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久后消失在这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.94,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得透明…消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.25,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回家了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:16.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.70,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:22.60,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我已经无家可归了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:26.64,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到需要你的人的身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:30.59,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没人需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.62,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:41.87,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天放学后 你都会在音乐室里弹钢琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:47.67,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你并不知道 但我却一直在听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.47,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 你也抛弃了我 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:59.24,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不能再弹钢琴了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.51,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.76,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在听的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.34,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.78,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这样的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.72,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.36,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.57,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能做到十全十美就没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:20.83,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是第一就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:26.48,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来 我们要将大家都粉碎掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:30.70,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:33.71,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是会分不清谁是谁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.40,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后变成透明的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.46,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得透明…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:59.55,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 这样 我就自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.88,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 我就能从钢琴 从妈妈那里解脱出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.30,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:25.19,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我 我要变得透明 我要自由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:28.23,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 多蕗就是多蕗 没人能替代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.21,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 已经没有人需要我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:36.78,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢你啊  所以请不要变成透明的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.38,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我的身边来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.64,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来 我开始烧割生命线了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.82,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:53.45,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.51,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你的手会被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.01,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.27,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听话 快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.14,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有活下去的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:08.29,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就…为我而活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:22.17,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 我们一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.29,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.23,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 我们就是一样的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:39.39,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定是命运的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.27,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:09.30,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:19.75,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荻野目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.13,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:25.20,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:27.67,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.59,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 就这样别动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.65,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你可来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.93,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:41.14,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.75,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到 我也不知道他在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:52.99,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.47,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.62,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道爸爸在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道的事情我能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.14,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗老师 停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.92,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:21.27,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是没关系 就不知道他怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.83,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要报警
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:28.73,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 报警之后会有麻烦的可不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:30.52,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.30,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高仓冠叶 我知道你那些不可告人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:39.65,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道救你妹妹的那大笔钱 你是怎么到手的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:48.38,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(675,59)}这里是语音信箱 现在无法接听您的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:53.40,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,54)}请在哔— 声之后留下您的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.13,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马 你到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:54.40,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快接电话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.92,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬 究竟去哪儿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.96,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 什么时候收到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.77,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.88,0:12:17.90,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片 能将人们平时看不见的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.81,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意去看的事物拍摄下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:26.43,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 有时会拍到些出乎意料的有意思的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:33.16,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他们的残党混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.53,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而指挥他们的正是你的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.17,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的照片 什么也说明不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.43,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是天大的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.06,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:55.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.70,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到老爸之后你又想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.08,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是让他接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:05.89,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他偿还从我这里抢走的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:07.50,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:13.93,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母夺走了我在这世上最重要的人的生命 我是受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.82,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃果真的是个特别的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:33.07,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她还在 这世上的很多悲惨和不幸都可以避免
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:35.35,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃果是我们的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:45.54,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 本应成为人类的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.50,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么胡话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.35,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你父亲一手策划的事件也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:54.79,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃果曾试图阻止这一切的发生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:04.03,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却救不了所有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:10.36,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 桃果消失了 只留下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:14.05,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:15.49,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:22.48,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.85,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 你还是不叫你父亲过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:39.30,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.42,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的气势去哪儿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:46.06,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 我真的不知道父亲的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.59,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道 我肯定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹就这么重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.43,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:04.70,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 那就由你们来接受惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:09.22,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父债子还 天经地义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.96,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样 小冠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.27,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要救你妹妹 方法只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:40.16,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后那根绳索断裂时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.01,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的手去连接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.23,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬 抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.65,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马 你快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.18,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.91,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛吧 我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.14,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爱就是痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.73,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 该怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:37.93,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去 你的手可就废了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.24,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:43.35,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是家人 但你也不必太过自责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:46.99,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我母亲曾经对我那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:50.12,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不会放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.17,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃果…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:55.70,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗老师 快停下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:17:00.36,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果 现在的我很丑恶对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:06.86,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 桃果是那样拼命地救我 我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.81,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却成了现在这幅样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:14.68,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了桃果 也失去了我活下去的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:24.87,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在看到的 只是一只将我从内由外啃食干净的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.05,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.15,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 别再坚持了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.03,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.74,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:49.80,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠 够了 已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:54.20,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再为我付出那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.85,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经 足够
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:02.68,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:07.57,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 知道的 我的病已经治不好了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:10.31,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的日子也不多了 这些我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.76,0:18:12.03,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:14.24,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的病会好的 我会治好你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.86,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足够 我已经很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:26.82,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:32.04,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗老师 父亲的债就由我来偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:36.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请您放过小冠和小晶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.24,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:42.86,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小冠 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:47.45,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 小冠 从今以后 你要为了自己而活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:49.74,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:50.75,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.35,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:59.63,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要为你而活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.29,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:49.12,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:54.53,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果 你可不要步我的后尘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:56.80,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:19:59.57,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蕗老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:14.50,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.18,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳毬 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:21.08,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶马 你怎么这么慢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:23.43,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:29.26,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚已由我接受 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:31.24,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.83,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去医院 给阳毬用药…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.03,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.17,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:49.90,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得邀请了你 却错过了场好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:51.74,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你利用了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:54.26,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是碰巧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:57.88,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到 你会做出这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:02.68,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢 把他们俩叫出来目的何在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:13.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我们不过是冒牌的一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.15,0:21:16.13,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是相互利用而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.49,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:30.63,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了 得尽快摧毁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:36.36,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冠叶 我不能再让你待在那个家了 一刻都不能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.56,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:49.69,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我们并没有奢望过什么啊  只…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:57.20,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和他们不一样 我不会讨厌你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:22:01.58,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是悲伤还是痛苦 都不会是无用之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:04.68,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这就是命运 那就一定有它的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.07,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会接受着一切 然后变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:10.00,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:14.62,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,506)}所以 请为我活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:18.04,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法传达的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:22.25,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被撕裂的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:25.67,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛从未发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.50,0:22:28.73,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随云流走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:35.62,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰色星期三
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.78,0:22:38.74,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:42.45,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些闪闪发光的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:45.27,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是那么耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.38,0:22:48.86,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些坠入爱河的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:52.79,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:55.97,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起那些相爱的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.37,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起我们用那样认真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:02.88,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝视彼此的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.68,0:23:07.28,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 回想起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.60,0:23:09.71,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些闪闪发光的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:13.29,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些如梦般的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.55,0:23:16.96,Penguin_ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些相爱的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.49,0:23:29.35,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管接受怎样的惩罚 我都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:32.05,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我们不是已起过誓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.41,0:23:34.46,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:39.11,Penguin_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存战略 暂时还不要紧
